thread.title_full: RS Electrical Supplies reviewed by Clare

author: Clare
title: Clare
text:
Finally got around to replacing these bulbs. Website gave good explanations, I didn't have a clue what to search for really but found the right things easily and was able to work out from the descriptions that I needed a halogen bulb and a fluorescent one.
Delivery was quick, bulbs securely packaged - no breakages! Good quality, working fine. Can't fault.
